Instead spending your time complaining how hard it is to date in your town, or talking about how awful the opposite sex is, instead of feeling lonely, instead of trying to size up a human to a list of things you don’t want, what if you spent your time praying for the human you are manifesting, what if you started loving you by not investing your time into someone who isn’t adding to your best self, what if you let a moment spent live in the present. 

The constant of every experience you have in this life is you. Take ownership and stop settling for good enough!

❤️ love is the capacity to set someone free to open up their highest self by first investing in your full potential. If you find yourself trying to cage someone or yourself in under rules that limit one’s highest calling and nature I would say the emotion you think is love is really Fear in disguise.
-
Love is open not caged
-
Love is giving freely not conditionally
-
Love is because of who you are not the object of your love
- 
Love does not fear loss because it is impossible to lose her
-
Love does not chase love attracts
-
Love is the sound of life

This day Dec. 28, 2020 shifted an energy in me that needed to be woke the fuck up. When I was in LA a few days ago the detectives from my case back in 2020 called and said they think they had found the guy who held me up. As i waited for them to arrive i thought man am i going to feel sad, mad, hurt, satisfied, i really didn’t know. But as i looked at the images of the possible suspects all i could feel and think about was empathy and gratitude for the life i have and for the men in each photo. We are not promised anything but to be born and to die in this human experience. I am just so honored for everything in this life, The people, and for having another day to thrive in it. We will forever have hard times. It’s what you do with those that can change the entire outcome of your future. You have a gift and it’s special and you are needed, wanted, loved and highly favored. Thank you for being here.
